params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard shows Host Profile overview related to the Prisma Cloud Integration.
This dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of ingested host profile data.
It contains metric visualization which provides the total count of host profiles. It also provides information about host profiles by the distribution of host profiles over time and app, allowing you to track the growth or changes in your host profiles.
It also provides details on the top 10 listening ports and outgoing ports in your host profiles.
It also helps you identify the geographic distribution of SSH events.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/prisma_cloud/overview)**
